\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 How many would you have for a bridge party?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid13720733\charrsid6102048 
