\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 No, only dinner parties. These military people, they would often give a dinner party for about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
