\insrsid4799013\charrsid6102048 4}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048  of them, and I couldn't really ... didn't ought to spend the money for them but they were cheap, 3/6d. each and there were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid4799013\charrsid6102048 4}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048  of them. I can't think of the titles of the others, and we bought the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4799013\charrsid6102048 4}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 . And I've lent them out. Now, I've only got one. They don't return them, you see.
