\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 After you stopped going to Sunday School, did you ever see a poem you liked and learn it for the pleasure of it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Oh, yes, yes, I have, yes. yes. But I couldn't keep them here like my husband.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 He's amazing, yes. Did you ever learn anything or ready anything of }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4488453\charrsid6102048 Rudyard}
{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048  Kipling?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 No.
