He wrote a poem called 'If', which was very famous at one time. 'If you can keep your head when all about you are losing theirs and blaming it on you.. I wondered if you'd ever heard of it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Did you buy and read any newspapers or magazines?
