\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 That's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Do you know any books that they read to them there? Can you remember?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 No, I don't. I remember some books my mother bought and I can't think how she could afford it. She bought - a
nd I believe I've got it now - The Bible and The Newspaper, and another one was The Holy }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11677498\charrsid6102048 W}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 
ar, I don't know what that's like ... and Pilgrim's Progress, I've read that through to my father at times. I can't stick that book, Pilgrim's Progress, it's so complicated think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 And your father used to like you to read to him, did he?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Could he read himself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 No, not really, he was no scholar. He didn't have any schooling. I believe he went to school and didn't he used to tell you, 
Bobby, that he left school when he was what? 12? When he could work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mr. J: Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mrs. J: At 12, yes, yes. But he used to like me to read that to him.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Did you read to your mother, too?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 No, Mother used to like to read on her own. She'
d put her glasses on and then we children made a noise she said 'oh, will you keep quiet', she'd say. Mother loved reading, but there wasn't much time for her to do it, really.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Did she encourage you in your interest in reading?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Oh, well, yes, she did really, but she couldn't afford to buy us books. No no, she couldn't.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Did any of your brothers and sisters also read?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 My sister didn't read a lot, she didn't like it. But my youngest brother, well, both of them, didn't they? (aside to husb
and) They used to like reading, yes. Well, I'd like it now, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11677498\charrsid6102048 but I can't get interested. You\rquote re}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048  mi}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11677498\charrsid6102048  (?)}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048  as we get older, you see, we get so - get a bit perplexed, and that sort of thing and you can't just cope with it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 I didn't have time to ask you last
 week about school. I have some idea of what the school was like, you know, from what your husband said, but from your point of view, can you describe to me what the school was like? How you found it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Well, I rather liked it after I got used to it. We went when we were }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11677498\charrsid6102048 5}{
\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 
 and when we first went to school, when I think of it now, we used to do the most stupid things. Stupid. They used to give us newspapers to tear up in little pieces. Do you remember that? (aside to husband)
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mr. J: Yes, oh, yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mrs. J: I was just in the infants.</subject2>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Why did they give you that, do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 
Well, I should think they - I was given to understand they stuffed cushions with it. You see, a newspaper - just for... not all day we didn't 
do that, but just sometimes. Then after that we used to have some paper or some pencils or crayons to draw something or give something to draw. And then as we got up we had to learn arithmetic, you see, counting up just few figures. We called that Arithme
tic Lesson. And then we used to have reading lesson and on and on. Then one afternoon did needlework.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 When you learnt arithmetic, did you have paper and pencils or did you have slates?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Oh, slates. We had slates, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Do you remember how you learnt to count and do figures? How did the teacher teach you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 
Well, she had a blackboard on an easel, and put it on there, you see, and we had to copy it out, a sum, perhaps. And then the... the figures of the sum and then count it up, and then she'
d come and see who was right and who wrong and put the right answer on the board. We all didn't get it right - that when we were very young, when we first went.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Did you have anything like beads or counters?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Yes, a frame with beads on - counting - one line counting, one way and another, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 And writing, did you spend much time on learning writing?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 
Well, we did, I think, but I'm not sure if ever we had to print. But I couldn't get on very well with writing. The teacher used to write so
mething on the board and we had to copy that off on to our slate. Then she'd come see, you see, if it was all right. 'Course, they were the right words that she put on ... the right letters that we'd got to do, but the thing was we hadn't made them proper
ly, you see. That's it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 And you say you had dictation. Did you ever have to make up a story.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 
No, no. Like an essay? No. They used to read us a piece out and we had to write that down when we had an examination, in an exercise book, and - pencil, 
or ink I think we had, and that - well, I can see my writing now, got 'excellent' for that. They'd come along and put 'ex' against it and I thought 'My heavens. My!' But I didn't keep it like that after I left school I can tell you. I used to write better
 than I do now. Shocking now, I think.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 And do you remember if they had any monitors?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Oh, yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Tell me about them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Well, they used to come round and they didn't know what they would teach us, and we were - I'm afraid we were r
ude to them sometimes. If we were told do anything, we wouldn't do it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 So they didn't know what they were teaching, did you say?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 No. They were just monitors, just some of the oldest girls and boys in school. Yes, that's it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 How were they chosen?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 
Well, I don't know, I suppose they - the headmaster or mistress, I suppose would choose them as being some of the best scholars. I was never chosen.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Would you have liked to have been, though?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 No. Oh, no, I wouldn't!
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 And did they spend a lot of time, these girls and boys, trying to teach the younger ones?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 
No, they'd come and look and see if we'd got anything to do - see what we'd done on our slates, you see, and if it wasn't right, they'd just tell us to rub it all out and write something more, you see.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 How many of them were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Oh, they'd have about - perhaps if there was a - well, if there was a big class they'd have, perhaps, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid11677498\charrsid6102048 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048  girls and perhaps a couple of boys.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 How many other children would there be in the class then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 
Oh, well, I don't know how many there'd be now. Not big classes. Well, the school that we went to, if they'd got a whole, really a full supply, a full attendance, there would be about 300. Would there, Bob?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mr. J: I never knew - I knew 225.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mrs. J: It was always put up on the slate how many was there.</subject2>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 
Yes, I remember you told me. I've got that down. 225. Well then, how many would there be, say, all under one teacher, have you any idea? I think you said there were about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8405883\charrsid6102048 4}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 
\ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048  teachers, were there? There was the schoolmaster and his wife.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 The schoolmaster didn't have a class. He only kept the cane.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Didn't he teach?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 No, no, he never did. He and his wife lived in the school house. He'd just sit th
ere and march from one room to the other. The Governess, his wife, she taught, and then there was Miss Bass, Miss Waller, Miss - well, there were about }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8405883\charrsid6102048 3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048  or }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8405883\charrsid6102048 4}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 
 other teachers, that's all. The wife, the schoolmaster wife, the Governess we used to call her, s
he was in the infant room and then she had a teacher with her in the infants, and they kept in the infants. I think, 'till they were going on for 6, then they went into what they call the no standards.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Would there have been more children in the infants than there would be, say, in the single standards?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Well, I - yes, I should almost think, when they first went, you see, first went at 5. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Did you get any prizes at school? You mentioned prizes at Sunday School.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 No, I never did. No, the - no, was there any prizes?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mr. J: No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 No prizes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 
Mrs. J: There used to be what they called the Ardleigh Show, the village show, and the knitting and needlework from the school, they could put that it My sister, she got a prize for kni
tting a pair of socks, but that was... that belonged to the school. But whoever knitted it got the prize. They had the money for it, you see.</subject2>
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 How much did she get, do you know?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Well, I think she got 1/6. That's all, for knitting - 'c
ourse, she didn't find the wool, that was found at the school, you see. I got a prize for blackberries and wild flowers once, a collection of wild flowers, and a dish of blackberries. That's all I got. I couldn't knit or sew nicely.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Was that all through the school that you got your prize?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Well, no, it was at the Show.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Yes, but I mean, like your sister, you said, sent hers through the school. Was yours also sent through the school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Yes, it was sent through the school, yes. yes. And then
, you see, they becomes the school's property. And after that they were sold, if anybody'd like to buy them. Same with my sister. I don't suppose they were bought because Mother had got no use for them. They were priced and then the teacher said 'well ...
.' the price of them, and if anybody wanted to buy them, they could}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11677498\charrsid6102048 .}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048  They could buy them.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 And were they sold? Do you know? Your sister's things?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Oh, yes, there was always somebody ready, the people that were better off the Father and Mother and they could afford it.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 And what happened to that money, then, that the people paid when they bought
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Well, that went into the school, you see, to buy more wool to knit other things.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Were your things sold? Your flowers and blackberries?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 O
h, no, they were our own. We gathered them, you see. We went and gather them in the field. I think I got 2/- for the dish of blackberries, best dish of blackberries and a shilling - third prize for wild fruits and flowers a shilling.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 So you kept that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 
We kept that money, yes, of course, and the things too, but they were not much good afterwards. See, they didn't cost me anything, did they. They didn't cost Mother anything.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 All profit?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 That's right, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Can you tell me more about the Ardleigh Show, what it was like?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 
Well, it was a very good show. Very good show. People used to put things out of their cottage gardens, and prizes for various potatoes, the }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8405883\charrsid6102048 12}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048  best and then cabbages, and apples, best dish of dessert apples, and all - it was a wonderful show for a country village, wasn't it? Wonderful.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mr. J: Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Do they still have it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Hasn't been for years, has it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mr. J: Not like our day. They do have a sort of show, but they don't have it on a meadow, or 
anything like that. I think they have it at the school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mrs. J: The British Legion, I think, run that.</subject2>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 The one when you were a girl, where was that held?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Oh, on a park just before you get to Ardleigh Station. On a park. A wonderful turn-out, it was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Out in the open air, then?}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid11677498\charrsid6102048 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Both: Yes, oh, yes, yes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 And what else happened at the show, was it just the produce out, or were the entertainments?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 We used to have a catalogue, you see, to see what you could en
ter for the show, and you had to pay - anything you entered you had to pay 2d. or 3d. to enter it. And then you stood a chance you got a prize. A prize for homemade cakes and sandwiches; homemade bread; homemade jam.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Did your mother enter?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 No, Mother never put anything in like that, no. Never, never.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Did men put things in, too?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Yes, things from the garden - potatoes, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mr. J: And the noise! (laughter)
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mrs. J: You never put anything in, did you?</subject2>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mr. J: No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mrs. J: He didn't bother, no.</subject2>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 You said when you were at Little }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid4488453\charrsid6102048 Bromley}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048  Hall and you had your bicycle, life was very much nicer 'cos you could bike home. When did you get your bicycle.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Well, I had that when I was at Berechurch, didn't I?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 
You said when you were at Fridaywood Lodge - that was near Berechurch way you said then that you didn't have one, thought, I think you told me.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mr. J: That'd be the time, yes. No, she didn't have a bicycle at Fridaywood Lodge.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mrs. J: Didn't I?</subject2>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mr. J: No, you didn't. No, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 You said you couldn't get home very easily.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mrs. J: I can't remember, then. I know I'd got it when I was at Little Bromley Hall.</subject2>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Do you remember buying it? I mean, was it a big event for you to get a bicycle?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Oh, no, I don't think - it was only a secondhand one, was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mr. J: Secondhand one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mrs. J: It was only }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid1710819 \'a3}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 
4.</subject2>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Did you buy it yourself?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 I don't know, I'm not sure. Do you, Bob?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mr. J: I don't know (laughter)
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Might it have been a present, do you think?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Oh, I don't know if I did buy it, did I?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mr. J: I don't know. I know you had one.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 K2  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Mrs. J: I think I did. Oh, no, it wasn't a new one, of course. No, Oh, dear me, no.</subject2>
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 And before you had your bicycle, how would you get home, then, to see your parents?
