u liked very much. I was wondering what were the differences between places?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 Well, I don't know if that could have been when I was at Nicholson's for over a year.
