\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 I got the impression that it was somewhere local, quite near, you know.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 
Yes, I think I remember somebody of the name of Murrants, it was called. Murrants, that's the place. That was rough, but they were - they were very common people. But they were a big family of them and }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\insrsid8405883\charrsid6102048 2}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048  of the young ladies, Margery and - they went to boarding school for the week in Colchester.
