 the horses up after I'd been with them }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid8801673\charrsid6102048 5}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048  years.
