It was my own choice. He'd have done anything if I hadn't gone. I had to know more about - I got just so I could do me work. You see, you can't take a plough - I couldn't take a plough and a pair of horses and go and do so-and-so, you w
ant an education same as anyone do for that. Anyway, I left a I went anywhere where I could get a job. And that's the time, between that time and I went thatching, I done the work at Ardleigh Park.
