\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid16072274 AJ  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 The lawns. In 1907, the old gentleman what done the thatching and that, lid he sent for me to know if I'd go to work for him.
