\insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 . That's how that was.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 But how was it that you got a shilling more? Was it because you were better
