\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid3289702 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \insrsid14893121\charrsid6102048 What about the old farmer you first work for, did he try to influence the me at all, do you think?
